            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3 col-md-3">
            <div class="boxShadow1 homefooter">
                <h3><i class="fa fa-users fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i> Join Our Network</h3>
                <p>Foodready.net can help restaurant to increase food sales and market online. </p>
                <p><br /><a class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" href="~/Partners" role="button"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-asterisk"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; Learn more</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-3 col-md-3">
            <div class="boxShadow1 homefooter">
                <h3><i class="fa fa-2x fa-headphones" aria-hidden="true"></i> Get Help</h3>
                <p>Questions? Live Chat with one of our representatives, all time support.</p>
                <p><br /><a id="btn-chat" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" href=" " role="button"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-asterisk"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; Chat support</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>